  "notes": [
    "This study examined ethnic disparities in male breast cancer between Han and Mongolian populations in Inner Mongolia, China",
    "The study found no significant ethnic disparities in disease burden and healthcare utilization overall",
    "BRCA mutations, particularly BRCA2, were identified as important risk factors for male breast cancer"
